The INE eJPT certification is an entry-level certification in Cybersecurity for "Red Teamers" (offensive) / pentesters.
It is  a 100% pratical hands-on certification for pentesters. 
Their learning path is awesome!

THE LEARNNIG PATH PTS (Penetration Testing Student) - recommended to do before taking the exam - is totally FREE!


References:
https://elearnsecurity.com/product/ejpt-certification/
