Duration of exam : 72h (pratical exploitation + send the report before 72h after you have launched the exam)
NO PREREQUISITES
Exam cost : 200$

eJPT & Me:
I scored 95% and has taken the exam in 12h with some long breaks and double(triple) checked all answers before sending.
In few words : I have taken all my time!







